OL,3,CReport finds 'failings' in case of
OL,4,Cbanned driver left free to kill
OL,6,FProbation officials failed to take
OL,7,Faction against a driver who repeatedly
OL,8,Fbreached a motoring ban before he
OL,9,Fkilled a young biker in a hit-and-run,
OL,10,Fa report has revealed.
OL,12,FShane Kelk, who had 22 previous
OL,13,Fconvictions, including for driving
OL,14,Foffences, collided head-on with Amy
OL,15,FCooper's motorcycle near Holbeach,
OL,16,FLincolnshire, in 2022.
