OL,3,CReport finds 'failings' in case of
OL,4,Cbanned driver left free to kill
OL,6,FHe fled the scene as she lay dying but
OL,7,Fwas arrested and later jailed for
OL,8,Feight years and three months for a
OL,9,Frange of offences, including causing
OL,10,Fdeath by dangerous driving and driving
OL,11,Fwhile banned.
OL,13,FIt later emerged that Kelk was on
OL,14,Flicence at the time of the crash.
OL,16,FA review shared with Amy's family last
OL,17,Fyear laid out a catalogue of failings
OL,18,Fin the probation service's supervision
OL,19,Fof Kelk before the collision.
