OL,6,FAmy's mother, Amanda Cooper, said
OL,7,Fcoming to terms with the report's
OL,8,Fcontents was like losing Amy all over
OL,9,Fagain.
OL,11,FShe told ITV News: "There are so many
OL,12,Finstances where they didn't supervise
OL,13,Fhim properly, he was allowed to get
OL,14,Faway with not attending meetings and
OL,15,Ffor us, crucially, they ignored the
OL,16,Ffact that he was driving illegally.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
