OL,3,CReport finds 'failings' in case of
OL,4,Cbanned driver left free to kill
OL,6,F"And it's clear from reading the
OL,7,Freview, that not only should he never
OL,8,Fhave been driving at all, he shouldn't
OL,9,Fhave been at liberty - he should have
OL,10,Fbeen recalled to prison."
OL,12,FAmy's sister, Sam Pointon added: "At
OL,13,Fone point soon after being released
OL,14,Ffrom prison in 2020, he was caught
OL,15,Fdriving while on drugs and he was
OL,16,Fconvicted of that the following May.
OL,17,FThe probation service were supposed to
OL,18,Fat least send a letter of notification
OL,19,Fsaying he had breached his licence -
OL,20,Fthey didn't do that.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
