OL,3,CReport finds 'failings' in case of
OL,4,Cbanned driver left free to kill
OL,6,F"On another occasion he crashed into a
OL,7,Ftree and it wasn't brought to anyone's
OL,8,Fattention. There are so many examples
OL,9,Fwhere they knew he was driving.
OL,11,F"There is a systemic issue here and
OL,12,Fthis driver should never have been in
OL,13,Fthe position to do what he did that
OL,14,Fnight. And the result is the traumatic
OL,15,Fdeath of my sister who really
OL,16,Fsuffered. And our lives will never be
OL,17,Fthe same."
