OL,4,Cbanned driver left free to kill
OL,6,FFollowing the review Amanda Cooper
OL,7,Fcalled on the coroner to reopen the
OL,8,Finquest into Amy's death. Her request
OL,9,Fwas declined.
OL,11,F"He said there was nothing in the new
OL,12,Fmaterial I gave him that suggested his
OL,13,Fmere presence on the road presented a
OL,14,Freal and immediate risk to life,"
OL,15,FAmanda said.
