OL,3,CReport finds 'failings' in case of
OL,4,Cbanned driver left free to kill
OL,6,FIn a statement it said: "This was a
OL,7,Fterrible crime and our thoughts remain
OL,8,Fwith the family and friends of Amy
OL,9,FCooper. While serious further offences
OL,10,Fare rare, they have a devastating
OL,11,Fimpact and we take each one extremely
OL,12,Fseriously.
OL,14,F"We have taken action to address these
OL,15,Fissues, including reviewing the
OL,16,Fguidance for probation staff on
OL,17,Fassessing the risk posed by serious
OL,18,Fdriving offenders."
